            "text": "Not only does this Packard exude grace with its smooth exterior design, when it debuted car shoppers remarked it was like riding on a “magic carpet.” That ultra-comfortable ride dynamics is afforded by five airplane-type shock absorbers as well as a lateral stabilizer, a setup which for the time was unusual.",
